rows.label: qst201321_msg0001
rows.name:
Where were you planning
to take the children?

rows.label: qst201321_msg0003
rows.name:
...Staying silent will do you no
good. Where were you taking them?

rows.label: qst201321_msg0005
rows.name:
We were asked to kidnap
children from various nations
and bring them there.

rows.label: qst201321_msg0006
rows.name: Asked? So there are others involved?

rows.label: qst201321_msg0007
rows.name:
Of course. It'd be impossible
for us to kidnap children from
every nation by ourselves.

rows.label: qst201321_msg0011
rows.name: Then I will ask another question.

rows.label: qst201321_msg0012
rows.name: Why were you kidnapping the children?

rows.label: qst201321_msg0014
rows.name:
Our job was just to hand them
over to the client and get paid.

rows.label: qst201321_msg0015
rows.name:
We don't care what they
do with the children.

rows.label: qst201321_msg0010
rows.name:
Everyone, let's go to Port
Ananyam in Superbia and
investigate immediately.
